    <title>基于Qt进行光学系统仿真及测量系统软件的开发</title>
    <url>/2023/06/17/qtwork/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>菲涅尔双棱镜干涉测波长</p>
<p>菲涅尔双棱镜干涉是一种分波面干涉方法。菲涅尔双棱镜可以看成是两块底面相接、棱角很小的直角棱镜合成。若置单色光源S0于双棱镜正前方，则从S0射来的光束通过双棱镜的折射后，变成两束相重叠的光，这两束光仿佛是从光源S0的两个虚像S1和S2射出的一样。由于S1和S2是两个相干光源，所以在两束光重叠区域可观察到明暗相间的干涉条纹。通过干涉条纹测出光源的波长。</p>
<span id="more"></span>
<p>所用到的仪器及参数如下。<br>菲涅尔双棱镜：顶角37’，折射率n&#x3D;1.5163</p>
<p>线阵相机：<br>CCD芯片采用东芝TCD1304AP，像素大小为8μm×200μm，像素共3648，波长响应范围为300nm～1100nm。AD采样速率：187.5kHz，AD采样深度：16Bit。USB 2.0接口，所用USB接口芯片为FT245，最高通讯速率为1MByte。CCD的积分曝光时间100级可调，积分时长10μs-1ms。内触发时所设置的CCD输出帧率为50帧&#x2F;秒。<br>此CCD 共有3648 个感光元，这些感光元的总长度约为29.1mm，从CCD 芯片左侧6.25mm 起至35.35mm 范围为有效光照范围，因此CCD 芯片左右两侧约6mm 范围是不应该受到光照射的，应该做适当遮挡。<br>对CCD 的控制命令是通过向FT245RL 发送（或者说写入）字符串完成的，主要字符串命令如下：<br>“#?data%” : 获取CCD 3648 个像元的强度；<br>“#CCDInt:nnn%” : 设置积分时间，这里nnn代表001~100 范围内的100 个数值（注意这里的0不能省略），代表积分时间为nnn 毫秒。<br>在计算机向FT245RL 发送字符串#?data%后，CCD 会立即向计算机发送3648*2 个unsigned char类型的字符串，这些字符串中每两个字符（每个字符8Bit）形成一个unsigned short（16Bit）型的数字共3648 个，分别代表CCD 各个像元的光强度。</p>
<p>光源：波长未知，约0.6微米左右</p>
<p>下面是串口部分相关代码</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">void MainWindow::<span class="function"><span class="title">findport</span></span>()</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    foreach(const QSerialPortInfo &amp;info, QSerialPortInfo::availablePorts())</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        QSerialPort serial;</span><br><span class="line">        serial.setPort(info);   //设置串口</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(serial.open(QIODevice::ReadWrite))</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            ui-&gt;serialbox-&gt;addItem(serial.portName());        //显示串口name</span><br><span class="line">            serial.close();</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">void MainWindow::<span class="function"><span class="title">on_openbtn_clicked</span></span>()</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    update();</span><br><span class="line">    Sleep(100);      //延时100ms</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(!serialopen)</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        findport();     //重新查找串口</span><br><span class="line">        //初始化串口</span><br><span class="line">        serialport-&gt;setPortName(ui-&gt;serialbox-&gt;currentText());        //设置串口名</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(serialport-&gt;open(QIODevice::ReadWrite))              //打开串口成功</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            serialport-&gt;setBaudRate(9600);       //设置波特率</span><br><span class="line">            serialport-&gt;setDataBits(QSerialPort::Data8);        //设置数据位为8位</span><br><span class="line">            serialport-&gt;setParity(QSerialPort::NoParity);       //设置校验位为无校验</span><br><span class="line">            serialport-&gt;setStopBits(QSerialPort::OneStop);      //设置停止位为1位</span><br><span class="line">            serialport-&gt;setFlowControl(QSerialPort::NoFlowControl);     //设置流控制</span><br><span class="line">            //连接槽函数</span><br><span class="line">            QObject::connect(serialport, &amp;QSerialPort::readyRead, this, &amp;MainWindow::ReadData);</span><br><span class="line">            // 设置控件可否使用</span><br><span class="line">            ui-&gt;openbtn-&gt;setText(<span class="string">&quot;关闭串口&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">            serialopen = <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span>    //打开失败提示</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            Sleep(100);</span><br><span class="line">            QMessageBox::information(this,<span class="built_in">tr</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Error&quot;</span>),<span class="built_in">tr</span>(<span class="string">&quot;打开失败&quot;</span>),QMessageBox::Ok);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">     &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        serialport-&gt;clear();        //清空缓存区</span><br><span class="line">        serialport-&gt;close();        //关闭串口</span><br><span class="line">        serialopen = <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        ui-&gt;openbtn-&gt;setText(<span class="string">&quot;打开串口&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>数据处理部分</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">void MainWindow::<span class="function"><span class="title">ProcessData</span></span>()</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    int threshold = 21000;      //阈值</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (int i = 0; i &lt; 3600; ++i)</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (Data[i] &gt; threshold)</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            Data[i] = 1;  // 大于阈值的置为1</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            Data[i] = 0;  // 小于阈值的置为0</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    Paint(Data0, Data);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    int a;</span><br><span class="line">    int b;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(int i=1000;i&lt;1200;i++)      //寻找条纹左边界，1000和1200是检测范围，根据实际图像改</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(Data[i+1]-Data[i] == 1)//&amp;&amp;(Data[i+5]-Data[i] == 1))</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            a = i+1;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(int i=1950;i&gt;1700;i--)      //寻找条纹右边界，1950和1700是检测范围，根据实际图像改</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(Data[i]-Data[i-1] == 1)</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            b = i;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    int x = b-a;</span><br><span class="line">    int peakCount = 0;</span><br><span class="line">    int shuzu[300];</span><br><span class="line">    int j=0;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (int i = 1000; i &lt; 1900; ++i)</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (Data[i] &gt; Data[i-1] &amp;&amp; Data[i] == Data[i+1])    //大于前一个数且等于后一个数</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            shuzu[j]=i;</span><br><span class="line">            ++peakCount;</span><br><span class="line">            j++;</span><br><span class="line">            //break;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">float</span> D = ui-&gt;Dbox-&gt;text().toFloat();</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">float</span> L = ui-&gt;Lbox-&gt;text().toFloat();;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">float</span> H = 2*L*0.01076*0.5163;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">float</span> delta = (<span class="built_in">float</span>)(8*x)/(<span class="built_in">float</span>)(peakCount-1);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">float</span> lambda = delta*(H/D);</span><br><span class="line">    QString strlambda = QString::number(lambda);</span><br><span class="line">    ui-&gt;mesrvalue-&gt;setText(strlambda);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>其余数据收发，绘图等代码不再展示。<br>整个结果如下：<br><img src="/2023/06/17/qtwork/result.png"></p>
<p>此外，此软件还可用来完成单光源投影法测量细丝直径，激光衍射法测量细丝直径，<br>除数据处理部分不同外，其他内容都相似。</p>
]]></content>
